{"tid":1590033,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Twitter 文宣組同我入黎.....","createTime":"2019-09-23T14:03:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T15:01:10.000Z","uid":185424,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"6281199d4b80f0f9a3e81f6d1874e87681075589","tid":1590033,"uid":185424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T14:03:38.000Z","msg":"Twitter 呢排大家都好努力....成績係有目共睹<br />\n雖然我覺得有時都係自己人圍爐多, 但我相信尊貴的congressmen 都感受到我地的誠意同對通過Hong Kong Human Rights and Freedom Act 的決心....<br />\n但係有另外一條戰線- Youtube, 我地從來無認真對付過, 而家 d五毛多撚到, 我以為自己睇緊垃圾微博....自己睇圖...<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Youtube</span></span></strong> 大家都識玩, 唔使教, 不外乎都係LIKE 下大家啱聽的comment, 又唔使貼圖, hashtag, 純文字comment....Youtube 唔同Tweet....Tweet 沉得快...但Youtube 係度一世....d 五毛comment 一樣係度一世.....<br />\n目測五毛重災區係<strong>bbc news</strong> 同<strong>The New York Times.</strong>....<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>大家幫下手, 開多個youtube account, 同五毛開場鍵盤戰</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pCNJyBd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpCNJyBd.jpg&h=fcbaf4ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o7i1kgd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo7i1kgd.jpg&h=ec461b9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LiETbnU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLiETbnU.jpg&h=8b461f2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SETD6We.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSETD6We.jpg&h=1c4f0327&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"53ba6bedbfe2d16ebff9cde88f1f3773214acf89","tid":1590033,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T14:03:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢